NEWELL
v.
N.C. DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC SAFETY 347P17-1 Supreme Court of North Carolina. December 7, 2017 Jonathan James Newell, for Newell, Jonathan James. Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, for N.C. Department of Public Safety, et al. Robert S. Banks, District Attorney, for the State.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 18th of October 2017 by Petitioner for Petition for Discretionary Review:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 7th of December 2017."
